+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01VVSGVz2auWzAhK6cTyDswt","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've now read all the required source files. Let me create a comprehensive summary of the codebase structure and contents.\n\n## CODEBASE EXPLORATION SUMMARY\n\n### 1. DIRECTORY STRUCTURE\n```\n/workspace\n├── src/\n│   ├── db.ts          (Database creation and seeding)\n│   ├── models.ts      (TypeScript interfaces)\n│   ├── routes.ts      (Express routes for CRUD)\n│   ├── errors.ts      (Custom error classes and handler)\n│   ├── server.ts      (Express app factory)\n│   └── seed.ts        (Seed script entry point)\n├── tests/\n│   ├── search.test.ts (Full-text search feature tests - 20 tests)\n│   └── notes.test.ts  (CRUD operations tests - 15 tests)\n├── package.json       (Dependencies and scripts)\n├── tsconfig.json      (TypeScript configuration)\n├── vitest.config.ts   (Test configuration)\n├── .eslintrc.cjs      (ESLint configuration)\n└── TASK.md           (Task description)\n```\n\n### 2. KEY FILES CONTENTS\n\n#### **package.json**\n- **Name**: bench-fts-search\n- **Type**: ES Module\n- **Dependencies**:\n  - `better-sqlite3` (^11.0.0) - SQLite3 bindings\n  - `express` (^4.21.0) - Web framework\n- **Scripts**:\n  - `build`: tsc (TypeScript compilation)\n  - `lint`: eslint src/ tests/\n  - `test`: vitest run\n  - `seed`: tsx src/seed.ts\n- **Dev Dependencies**: TypeScript, Vitest, ESLint, TypeScript ESLint, Supertest, tsx\n\n#### **tsconfig.json**\n- **Target**: ES2022\n- **Module**: Node16\n- **Strict mode**: Enabled\n- **Output**: ./dist\n- **Includes**: src/**/*\n- **Excludes**: node_modules, dist, tests\n\n---\n\n#### **src/db.ts** (COMPLETE)\nProvides database initialization and seeding:\n\n**Functions**:\n1. `createDatabase(path?: string)` - Creates SQLite database with WAL journaling and foreign key constraints\n2. `seedDatabase(db)` - Populates database with 45 seed notes covering:\n   